channel.title: Help with my client
channel.description:
I was trying to convert my client into a webclient, and everything went well. So I jarred my client, and ran the jar, and got this error after the cache downloaded: [img]http://i739.photobucket.com/albums/xx32/float1234/Capture.jpg[/img] So, I was eager to find out what could have caused this, so I went back into my webclient folder and ran the .bat file that starts up the client, and I got this error in the CMD prompt: Error: loaderror Starting up 32
Please help! I don't have any money, so all I can do is rep++.
